title: Bug 121687: Exception throws when exporting data from a table inside a grid cell
OB: When exporting data from a table inside a grid cell, an exception is thrown.
EB: The export function should successfully export data from a table within a grid cell without throwing any exceptions.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
1. Insert a grid. 
2. Insert a table into one grid cell. 
3. Insert another table into another grid cell.
